display="inline"><![CDATA[X\in \mathcal {C}]]></fr:tex>, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {F}_X]]></fr:tex> be the category of quasi-coherent sheaves of modules on <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[X]]></fr:tex>.
    If <fr:tex
